sporting director has said that it might not

00:03:21.849 --> 00:03:27.430
be a one off, referring, jokingly, to last
years win. "We have shown before that we can

00:03:27.430 --> 00:03:38.439
annoy Bayern said their manager and maybe
they can do that again.

